 \Rightarrow \int \frac {-\sqrt{1 - (t-1)^2}}{t} = \int \frac {-\sqrt{t^2 + 2t}}{t} = \int \frac {-\sqrt t \cdot \sqrt t \cdot \sqrt{t + 2}}{\sqrt t \cdot t} 
